*Lepi* dan je danas. (It is a beautiful day today.)

On je *lepo* razmišljao o tome. (He was thinking about it nicely.)

Ona je *lepa* devojka. (She is a beautiful girl.)

Oni su *lepo* odrasli. (They have grown up nicely.)

*Lepši* je od njega. (She is prettier than him.)

Oni su napravili *lepu* zajednicu. (They made a beautiful community.)